This is a list of [[Portuguese television]] related events from 1996.

==Events==
*29 April - Canal 1 and TV2 revert to their original names as [[RTP1]] and [[RTP2]] with new logos.
*Unknown - José Nuno Martins takes over from [[Catarina Furtado]] as host of ''Chuva de Estrelas''.
*Unknown - Rui Faria Santos wins the third series of ''Chuva de Estrelas'', performing as [[Elton John]]. He becomes the first male finalist to have won.

